  "title": "URGENT! Lifestyle Store Managers (x5) | Up to $3000 + AWS + Commission",
  "description": "<p>📅 <strong>Start Date:</strong> ASAP (New Store Opening)<br />📍 <strong>Locations:</strong> Northpoint | Lentor<br /><br />We’re opening new stores across Singapore and are looking for <strong>dynamic and motivated Store Managers</strong> to join our growing retail family.</p><p>If you’re passionate about retail, enjoy leading a team, and take pride in delivering exceptional customer experiences, we’d love to meet you!</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>What You’ll Do:</strong></p><ul><li>Lead day-to-day store operations and ensure smooth workflow</li><li>Coach and motivate your team to achieve sales goals</li><li>Maintain high store standards and merchandising displays</li><li>Manage inventory and ensure accurate stock levels</li><li>Provide excellent customer service and handle escalated issues</li></ul><p><strong>What We’re Looking For:</strong></p><ul><li>2–3 years of retail experience with at least 1 year in a supervisory/managerial role</li><li>Strong leadership and communication skills</li><li>Customer-focused, hands-on, and results-oriented</li><li>Able to work retail hours, weekends, and public holidays</li></ul><p><strong>What We Offer:</strong></p><ul><li>Basic Salary From $2,700 + Allowances + AWS + Commission</li><li>Opportunity to grow with a fast-expanding retail brand<br /></li></ul><p><strong>📩 Apply Now</strong></p><p>Send your resume (MS Word format) to:</p><p>📱 WhatsApp / Telegram: 8509 0409</p><p>Please include your availability, notice period and expected salary in your application.</p><p><em>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</em></p><p>—</p><p>Annie Hoang (R25158747)</p><p>CREW by HRnet |HRnet Ventures Pte Ltd </p><p>EA24C2435</p>",
